author: @Gwen0902
content: I’m very happy for all the people that got to see her😊 Congratulations! I wish she would do some free concerts in the states. Also, I’m very happy that this commentator got it right!! She IS “THE QUEEN OF POP!!” I hate that other singers are trying to steal her title 😡 She has worked very hard through the years ❤️
